snippet.textDisplay:
words spoken tell you the truth 
no one wishes to comprehend, 
the fact that death is on the door, 
poverty and deprivation on the floor, 
and you keep laughing with your millions, 
just to stop breathing next moment, 
the last nano second figuring out, 
how to get out, 
alas it is not a system that can be compromised, 
eyes open, surprised and very much dead
could have done something instead,
worth you remembering for...
